  {
    title: "No Chemicals",
    description: "The goats eat the weeds. That's it. No spraying, no runoff, no worrying about what's getting into the water."
  },
  {
    title: "Quiet",
    description: "Ever tried to have a meeting with mowers running outside? Goats don't make that kind of racket."
  },
  {
    title: "Free Fertilizer",
    description: "What goes in must come out. The animals fertilize while they work. Your soil gets better, not worse."
