                Eden Grazing Services is a partnership between us at Soul Miner's Eden and Bo Carter, who's been doing this grazing thing for years. Here's how it breaks down:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span><strong>Bo Carter</strong> owns the goats and knows how to manage them. He's out there checking on them every day.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span><strong>Soul Miner's Eden</strong> handles the business side—quotes, scheduling, and making sure you're happy with the work.</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p class="font-medium text-warm-900">
                You get one point of contact and a crew that actually knows what they're doing.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Placeholder for partnership image -->
          <div class="bg-fuchsia-100 border-4 border-fuchsia-500 rounded-xl h-64 lg:h-80 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <p class="text-fuchsia-600 text-xs font-mono mb-2">PLACEHOLDER IMAGE</p>
              <p class="text-fuchsia-700 font-medium">Grazing animals photo</p>
              <p class="text-fuchsia-500 text-sm">(Add after pilot projects)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="text-center">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-600 to-accent-700 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-4">
          Want to Talk About It?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-accent-100 mb-8">
          We'll come out, look at your property, and tell you what we think. No pressure, no sales pitch—just an honest conversation about whether goats make sense for your situation.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/land-management/request" class="btn bg-white text-accent-700 hover:bg-accent-50 text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Request Free Assessment
          </a>
          <a href="/land-management/services" class="btn border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white/10 text-lg px-8 py-4">
            View Service Packages
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-accent-200">
          Or just call us at <a href="tel:{businessInfo.phone}" class="underline hover:text-white">(706) 613-4415</a>
